quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  111,1,"Gajonasiche makono ganagaŵili ga Abu Lahabi, nombe nao ajonasiche.",footnotes:320157:1
  111,2,"Ngaija kwakamuchisya ipanje yao atamuno yaŵapanganyisye (mpela ŵanache ŵaŵaŵeleche)."
  111,3,"Takajinjile ku Moto waukwete malamba (gakulapuka)."
  111,4,"Niŵankwao ŵakwe ŵaŵaliji nkutwichila sasu (syamiŵa nikuntejelaga Muhammadi ﷺ mwakupita)."
  111,5,"Nnukosi mwao (ŵele ŵakongweo) chimukaŵe mwana litondolo lyamiŵamiŵa (lyakwalagachisya nalyo)."
